{"tid":1884282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跑出必有因]新加坡政府神邏輯","createTime":"2020-02-17T13:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T12:21:07.000Z","uid":349653,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"05596eb5df3026891e8587ec97198657880e31bf","tid":1884282,"uid":349653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"新加坡政府同國民講有病唔舒服先戴口罩 因為缺貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aonCdQR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaonCdQR.png&h=349d188e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府有BCP計畫 不過係一半人返 rotate work from home 一星期 如果其中一個賴野 分一半都係一樣 細菌可以停留在office等下一更同事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lmao<br />\n<br />\nSet up alternate teams of employees (e.g. Team A &amp; Team B) who can be deployed at different work schedules (e.g. Team A working in the office at alternate weeks, while Team B telecommutes). The teams should be physically segregated to avoid the risk of infection between teams"},{"pid":"2984d6d1aaaf069c940e03e806aefeccc9006046","tid":1884282,"uid":77542,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"最鍾意睇坡佬仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b0315220fa7f87a566ef6eb84564779d40dd00","tid":1884282,"uid":55257,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"坡縣已經大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f3479061329ad5972405a1b411f26fb8ee055e","tid":1884282,"uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"坡佬係半個支那"},{"pid":"0d89ca080adc86b9bb7b0a71250077e34d23d0e6","tid":1884282,"uid":168567,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"林奠既意思都係咁<br />\n只係一個講出口 一個唔講出口"},{"pid":"26d0ac72ee8bfaeb9c6ec4bde42ddf4e6193a851","tid":1884282,"uid":171668,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,